'''South Korea''' is an original [[Nations|country]] that was on BitLife in September 2018. Its default cities are the capital, Seoul, along with Busan, Daegu, Gangnam, and Incheon. An [[achievements|achievement]] called ''K-Pop'' can be achieved for a character in South Korea who achieves [[fame]] as a singer.

==Name List==
South Korea is one of the few countries where people's names are backwards (the last name goes first), the others being [[Vietnam]] and [[Hungary]]. for example, "Park Hana". However, this occurs in the iOS version only. This is since names in these countries are given first.
